        yield return text(@"Without a moment's deliberation, we ambled through the entrance and buckled ourselves in. As we each tightened the buckles about us, we heard a loud hissing sound like the escaping of steam through unseen vents, and the door slammed shut. The metallic walls shook violently, jolting us against our constraints.");
