    {
        using (styleScope("bold", true))
        {
            yield return text("Escalation");
        }
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("As the war pressed on relentlessly, it was I who suffered most terribly. With emb" +
            "attlements requiring constant provisions, procuring the necessary ingredients fo" +
            "r my experiments became increasingly more difficult. ");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("However, in my humble brilliance I settled on a firm solution based upon one simp" +
            "le question: Why do I need specialty ingredients when I can just attach guns to " +
            "everything? ");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"Certainly this slapdash methodology was not ideal nor dignified, but it certainly achieved a devastative result. Why my first practical demonstration caused both sides to cease hostilities after witnessing a small battalion reduced to a mere wine stain upon the battlefield.");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"However, the regional military factions required additional convincing as the use of our weapons was still considered a ""war crime"" and would require further convincing to employ these additional methods. Imagine, ""science"" being considered a war crime? Is it not a general's hope to reach an efficient victory? ");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return link("Click here to continue...", "MartialSepEventa", null);
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield break;
    }


