            "pening.");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"We emerged from the mineshaft and made haste to the village. The changes were immediately obvious: The town had been returned to its former state, as it was in 1831. We knew that providence and some unseen benefactor had given us an opportunity to change the mistakes of the past and recreate a brighter future.");
