        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"I rushed to my Estate to be greeted by a familiar sight from my youth; the gothic iron and stone as formidable as I remembered. With a well-crafted farce, I introduced myself to my youthful parents as a relative on holiday. I quickly ingratiated myself into the fold and resolved to continue my experiments, searching for a way to return to my time, while also ensuring that history would not repeat itself.");
