        }
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"On a brisk April morning, our parents were called upon to attend another Town Hall meeting. Knowing full well the outcome, I summoned my cousins and concocted a simple plan to avoid the same mistake as the past. Using a mercurial and chloroform solution, our families were sufficiently lethargic upon the day in question and could not attend.");
