        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"I would never give it to them to abuse secretly at their discretion. No! But to publish it widely and allow all of the Hungarian people the chance to rewrite history? That, it seemed, would be the sort of experimental chaos the stuffed shirts at the university would never see coming!");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("But, perhaps, and most undoubtably, it would have untold repercussions.");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("The issue at hand, however, was the matter of secrecy. If any one of us - myself" +
            " or my dear cousins - decided to publish the schematic, it would be freely avail" +
            "able.");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("I knew that each would need to make their own private decision and I prayed that " +
            "it would be the correct choice.");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
