            yield return text(@"Releasing the Time Machine schematics had surprisingly little effect, or possibly it had an infinite number of consequences, which technically amounts to no effect at all. And if it did have an effect, I would certainly have no knowledge of the effect's effect as the timeline would have already twisted my knowledge of it. Suffice to say, with time travel, as with real life, everything and nothing matters.");
