        }
        yield return lineBreak();
        ViewGenerationEnding.instance.EnableDisableContinueBtn(true);
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"My close friends and family - many of whom I have permanently severed contact with because of their feelings on the matter - have expressed extreme misgivings about the publication of this book. They claim that my macabre fascination with exposing this to the world is unhealthy! ");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"Some have even derisively labeled this work as pseudoscience, homeopathy, or a drug-induced fever dream, but I say to them, ""who are you to criticize the moon and the stars for being in the sky?"" This work is important! How can they not see it? If anything, these outlandish experiments further prove the relevance of the science that is far better researched, performed, and peer-reviewed after publication in respected journals. ");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"For while the world may have sped onward at a pace that our scientific contributions could not match, rendering our innovations lame and timid in comparison, I believe that my family's failure to make an impact on a world of the future is an important lesson. Our contributions must be remembered, not for their value to the progress of mankind, but for laying the foundations of the work that others would ignore because of other more viable innovations which they could hone to perfection.");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("The world may have progressed beyond a need for mad science, but I believe it is " +
            "this spirit that will define my family\'s legacy. Even if what they did, does not" +
            ".");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text("THE END?");
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield break;
    }


