        {
            yield return text("Spiritualism Craze");
        }
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return lineBreak();
        yield return text(@"A fad of spirit rappings is spreading across the region and the royalty is being pressed by a regional temperance movement to outlaw this profane sport of seance. The advisor could not recall what a spirit rapping, a seance, or even note a time when he had witnessed a spiritualism meeting in the area, and the thought furrowed his brow severely. ");
